# What NOT to send to the docker daemon as part of the build context.
# Build context is project root, so paths are relative to it.

# === project-local scratch ===
tmp/

# === git + skill + editor ===
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
*.swp

# === Python caches / venvs ===
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/htmlcov
**/.coverage
**/.coverage.*
**/.venv

# === Frontend build artefacts ===
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.vite
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/e2e-screenshots
